Measure type: [717] Export control on restricted goods and technologies
Measure components: Condition [Y1] Other conditions : Document [C] Action [29] Import/export allowed after control : ||Condition [Y2] Other conditions : Document [Y] Action [29] Import/export allowed after control : ||Condition [Y3] Other conditions : Action [09] Import/export not allowed after control :
Conditions: CD975: (Conditions) A prior authorisation shall be required for the sale, supply, transfer or export, directly or indirectly, of the goods listed in Annex VII, whether or not originating in the Union, to any person, entity or body in Libya or for use in Libya (Article 2a, paragraph 1 of Council Regulation (EU) No 2016/44)  | CD976: (Conditions) The restriction shall not apply for the sale, supply, transfer or export, directly or indirectly, of goods listed in Annex VII, by authorities of Member States to the Libyan government or its agencies (Article 2a, paragraph 3 of Council Regulation (EU) No 2016/44)
